procstep.procdesc: This layer was created based on the 1:24000 National Hydropahy Dataset (NHD) flowing waters layer. The appropriate portions of the flowing waters were copied into the layer and merged based on the definition of each special regulation area. This resulted in one stream segment per each defined special regulation area.

qhorizpa.horizpae: Based on the 1:24000 National Hydrography Dataset (NHD) flowing waters layers

altsys.altenc: Explicit elevation coordinate included with horizontal coordinates

attrdomv.udom: Sequential unique whole numbers that are automatically generated.

attr.attrdef: County where lake or stream/river is located and regulated
Unique identifier for the water assigned by the PFBC (composed of the latitude and longitude location of the lake or latitude and longitude location of the mouth of the stream/river)
Water Resources Data System unique identifier for the water
Lower limit river mile of the special regulation section of the stream/river
Upper limit river mile of the special regulation section of the stream/river
